plot: In this insightful autobiographical mash-up of Super-8 home movies, vibrant animated cartography, and Dutch pidgin-speak, a family's 1981 vacation to the Kennedy Space Center is chronicled in exquisite detail.
title: 39-A: Een Reisverhaal Van Eindeloos
